Until next year of course!
This year&rsquo;s conference is done and Anastassia, Susan, and the wonderful Local arrangement folks at McGill are probably breathing a sigh of relief! Lots of informations was presented and some of it was absorbed! More will likely be reviewed over coming weeks preceded by the usual &ldquo;Now I know I saw a presentation about this at IASSIST&hellip;.&rdquo;
If you were one of those fine presenters, please don&rsquo;t forget to submit a paper to the IQ (instructions for doing so are on the IASSIST website).

